sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Consumidor as Consumidor / Aplicación
    participant API as API Exp Retiro Efectivo CBS <br> Epica 2668: RetiroEfectivoCBS <br> HU 7032: POST -  /correspondent-banking/v1/initiate-cash-withdrawal
    participant CL as Caché Local
    participant Lambda as Librería de parámetros <br> com.ficohsa.lib:regionalization <br> 2.4.2-SNAPSHOT
    participant Lib as Librería Phosteline (ConfigMap)
    participant lambdaCorr as Lambda Validación Corresponsales<br/> HU 7761 - ban-xrs-ic-lam-validate-bank-correspondent-{env}
    participant API1 as API Registra Transacciones Canal CB <br> Epica 2668: RetiroEfectivoCBS <br> HU 7034:  POST - /register-channel-transaction-status/v1/register
    participant API2 as API Limites Uso Servicio <br> Epica 2458: ConsultaCuentaRetiroEfectivoCBS <br> HU 6294:  POST - /controls-service-usage-limits/v1/initiate
    participant API3 as API Consulta Comisión CB <br> Epica 2668: RetiroEfectivoCBS <br> HU 7035:  POST - /retrieve-correspondent-commission/v1/retrieve
    participant API4 as API Realiza Retiro Efectivo <br> Epica 2668: RetiroEfectivoCBS <br> HU 62887:  POST - /execute-cash-withdrawal/v1/execute
    participant event as Event Bridge <br> integration-composition <br> ban-xrs-ic-te-evb-support-provider-responses-<env>
    participant API5 as API Actualiza Estado Transacción <br> Epica 2461: ConsultaEstadoTransaccionHN <br> HU 62321:  PUT /update-transaction-status/v1/update
    participant Errors as Control de Errores <br> Librería de mapeo de errores
    
    Note over Consumidor, Errors: Flujo Honduras (HN01) - API Consulta Comisión

    Consumidor->>API: REST Request
    Note right of Consumidor: Headers: <br> Branch-Id <br> body: <br> accountNumber, <br> currencyCode, <br> transactionAmount, <br> securityTokenReference, <br> transactionReferenceBC, <br> pointOfSale, <br> subPointOfSale

    API->>API: Validar Request
    Note over API: Valida campos obligatorios según contrato OpenAPI 

    API->>API: Validación exitosa

    alt Consulta parametros en caché local

        API->>CL: Consultar parámetros de Librería de parámetros en caché local
        Note right of API: Domain: "CORRESPONDENT_BANKING" <br> name: "INITIATE_CASH_WITHDRAWAL" <br> country: XRS 

        CL->>API: Obtiene parámetros de Librería de parámetros en Caché Local
        Note left of CL: Obtiene parámetros de regionalización y negocio
 
    else Consulta  parametros en Librería de parámetros / Parameter Store

        API->>Lambda: Consultar parámetros en librería de parámetros
        Note right of API: Domain: "CORRESPONDENT_BANKING" <br> name: "INITIATE_CASH_WITHDRAWAL" <br> country: XRS 

        Lambda->>API: Obtiene parámetros Librería de parámetros
        Note left of Lambda: Obtiene parámetros de regionalización y negocio

        API->>CL: Guarda parámetros lambda Parámetros en caché local
        Note right of API: Almacena parámetros de regionalización y negocio

    end

    API->>API: Validar Servicio Regional
    Note over API: Usando parámetros de regionalización obtenidos

    API->>API: Validación Regional success
    Note over API: Servicio habilitado para HN01 

    API->>Lib: Consulta Constantes
    
    Lib->>API: Retorna constantes necesarias
    Note left of Lib: Constantes: <br> caller-service

    API->>API: Construye request Lambda Valida Corresponsal
    Note over API: Mapeo: <br> correspondentPartyReference = header.Branch-Id, <br> country = request.header.soruceBank, <br> transactionType = libparam.transactionTypeT24

    API->>lambdaCorr: Consume Lambda Valida Corresponsal
    Note right of API: correspondentPartyReference, soruceBank, transactionType

    lambdaCorr->>API: Response Lambda Valida Corresponsal
    Note left of lambdaCorr: Response: <br> creditAccountReference, <br> debitAccountReference, <br> permittedCurrencyCode, <br> transactionType, <br> commissionAmount, <br> commissionCurrencyCode, <br> commissionTransactionType, <br> commissionAccountReference

    API->>API: Evalua response Lambda Valida Corresponsal

    alt If lambdaValCorr.success == false

        API->> Consumidor: Retorna error generado por lambda validación de corresponsal
        Note left of API: HTTP 4XX / 5XX

    else If lambdaValCorr.success == true

        API->>API: Evalua permittedCurrencyCode
        Note over API: permittedCurrencyCode = request.currencyCode <br> para continuar con el flujo

        alt If permittedCurrencyCode != request.currencyCode

            API->> Consumidor: Retorna error Moneda no permitida para este corresponsal
            Note left of API: HTTP 400: Moneda inválida

        else If permittedCurrencyCode == request.currencyCode        

            API->>API: Construye request API Registra Transacciones Canal CB
            Note over API: Headers: <br> sourcebank = header.sourceBank, <br> Branch-Id = header.Branch-Id <br> Body: <br> correspondentBankingAgentName = header.Application-Id, <br> transactionTypeCode = libparam.transactionType, <br> transactionStatus = libparam.transactionStatus, <br> transactionAmount = request.transactionAmount, <br> currencyCode = request.currencyCode, <br> transactionReferenceBC = request.transactionReferenceBC, <br> transactionReference = libparam.transactionReferenceT24, <br> transactionKeyReference = request.accountNumber, <br> pointOfSaleReference = request.pointOfSale, <br> subPointOfSaleReference = request.subPointOfSaleReference, <br> securityTokenReference = request.securityTokenReference, <br> commissionTransactionReference = libparam.commissionReferenceT24, <br> commissionAmount = responseValCorr.commissionAmount, <br> commissionCurrencyCode = responseValCorr.commissionCurrencyCode, <br> reversalTransactionReference = libparam.reversalTransactionReferenceT24

            API->>API1: Consume API Registra Transacciones Canal CB
            Note right of API: headers, body

            API1->>API: Response API Registra Transacciones Canal CB
            Note left of API1: Response: HTTP Code

            API->>API: Evalua response API Registra Transacciones Canal CB

            alt If HTTP Code != 200

                API->> Consumidor: Retorna error generado por API Registra Transacciones Canal CB
                Note left of API: HTTP 4XX / 5XX

            else If HTTP Code == 200

                API->>API: Construye request API Limites Uso Servicio
                Note over API: Body: <br> serviceName = const.caller-service, <br> user = header.Application-Id, <br> operationCode = libparam.operationCode, 

                API->>API2: Consume API Limites Uso Servicio
                Note right of API: serviceName, user, operationCode

                API2->>API: Response API Limites Uso Servicio
                Note left of API2: Response: HTTP Code

                API->>API: Evalua response API Limites Uso Servicio

                alt If HTTP Code != 200

                    API->>API: Construye mensaje para Event Bridge (API Actualiza Estado Transacción)
                    Note over API: Headers: <br> Application-Id = header.Application-Id <br> ++ Headers recibidos en la petición <br> Body: <br> transactionType = libparam.transactionTypeUpdate, <br> queryType = libparam.queryType, <br> transactionReference = request.transactionReferenceBC, <br> status = "CUOTA SERVICIO EXCEDIDA", <br> financialTransactionReference = "", <br> coreSystemTransactionReference = libparam.transactionReferenceT24, <br> paymentRecordUpdateType = libparam.updateType

                    API->>event: Envía evento a Event Bridge
                    Note right of API: Header, Body <br> Regla de enrutamiento para SQS <br> queueName: cola-api-actualiza-estado-transaccion-hn

                    event->>API5: Entrega Mensaje a API Actualiza Estado Transacción

                    API->> Consumidor: Retorna error generado por API Limites Uso Servicio
                    Note left of API: HTTP 4XX / 5XX

                else If HTTP Code == 200

                    API->>API: Construye request API Consulta Comisión CB
                    Note over API: Header: <br> Application-Id = header.Application-Id <br> Body: <br> transactionAmount = request.transactionAmount, <br> currencyCode = request.currencyCode, <br> correspondentTransactionTypeCode = libparam.transactionTypeT24 

                    API->>API3: Consume API Consulta Comisión CB
                    Note right of API: Header, Body

                    API3->>API: Response API Consulta Comisión CB
                    Note left of API3: Response: commissionAmount, <br> currencyCode

                    API->>API: Evalua response API Consulta Comisión CB

                    alt If HTTP Code != 200

                        API->>API: Construye mensaje para Event Bridge (API Actualiza Estado Transacción)
                        Note over API: Headers: <br> Application-Id = header.Application-Id <br> ++ Headers recibidos en la petición <br> Body: <br> transactionType = libparam.transactionTypeUpdate, <br> queryType = libparam.queryType, <br> transactionReference = request.transactionReferenceBC, <br> status = "ERROR OBTENIENDO COMISION", <br> financialTransactionReference = "", <br> coreSystemTransactionReference = libparam.transactionReferenceT24, <br> paymentRecordUpdateType = libparam.updateType

                        API->>event: Envía evento a Event Bridge
                        Note right of API: Header, Body <br> Regla de enrutamiento para SQS <br> queueName: cola-api-actualiza-estado-transaccion-hn

                        event->>API5: Entrega Mensaje a API Actualiza Estado Transacción

                        API->> Consumidor: Retorna error generado por API Consulta Comisión CB
                        Note left of API: HTTP 4XX / 5XX

                    else If HTTP Code == 200

                        API->>API: Construye request API Realiza Retiro Efectivo
                        Note over API: Body: <br> accountNumber = request.accountNumber, <br> currencyCode = request.currencyCode, <br> transactionAmount = request.transactionAmount, <br> securityTokenReference = request.securityTokenReference, <br> commissionAmount = responseValCorr.commissionAmount, <br> creditAccountNumber = responseValCorr.creditAccountNumber, <br> transactionTypeCode = responseValCorr.transactionType, <br> transactionReferenceBC = request.transactionReferenceBC, <br> commissionCurrencyCode = responseValCorr.commissionCurrencyCode, <br> commissionType = responseValCorr.commissionType, <br> commissionCreditAccountNumber = responseValCorr.commissionCreditAccountNumber

                        API->>API4: Consume API Realiza Retiro Efectivo
                        Note right of API: Header, Body

                        API4->>API: Response API Realiza Retiro Efectivo
                        Note left of API4: Response: <br> accountNumber, transactionAmount, currencyCode, <br> securityTokenReference, commissionAmount, transactionReference

                        API->>API: Evalua response API Realiza Retiro Efectivo

                        alt If HTTP Code != 200

                            API-->>event: No se envía evento desde API experiencia porque el evento de error lo envía la API de composición

                            API->> Consumidor: Retorna error generado por API Realiza Retiro Efectivo
                            Note left of API: HTTP 4XX / 5XX
                        
                        else If HTTP Code == 200

                            API->>API: Construye mensaje para Event Bridge (API Actualiza Estado Transacción)
                            Note over API: Headers: <br> Application-Id = header.Application-Id <br> ++ Headers recibidos en la petición <br> Body: <br> transactionType = libparam.transactionTypeUpdate, <br> queryType = libparam.queryType, <br> transactionReference = request.transactionReferenceBC, <br> status = "TRANSACCION EXITOSA", <br> financialTransactionReference = responseRealizaRetiroEfectivo.transactionReference, <br> coreSystemTransactionReference = libparam.transactionReferenceT24, <br> paymentRecordUpdateType = libparam.updateType

                            API->>event: Envía evento a Event Bridge
                            Note right of API: Header, Body <br> Regla de enrutamiento para SQS <br> queueName: cola-api-actualiza-estado-transaccion-hn

                            event->>API5: Entrega Mensaje a API Actualiza Estado Transacción

                            API->>Consumidor: Response Exitoso
                            Note left of API: HTTP 200: Response Body 
                        
                        end
                    
                    end
                
                end
            
            end

        end
    end 

    Note over Consumidor, Errors: Flujo Alternativo - Error
    activate API
    alt Exception occurs
        note over Errors: Error Library Handler
        activate Errors
            API->> Errors: Mapear código de error
            Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado
        deactivate Errors
        activate Consumidor
            API-->> Consumidor: Retorna error
        deactivate Consumidor
        Note over Consumidor,Errors: Diagrama guía de manejo de errores <br> http://bit.ly/4rpKVIU
    end
    deactivate API